{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_07_01",
  "title": "伊吹渚 1話 つむじで分かるんです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "home-office-01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "渚、お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ good work today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.6333332539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "夏のライブイベントの準備はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are the preparations for the summer live event going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8333332141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n練習は順調に進んでますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.\nPractice is going well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5661678791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ。ただ、ちょっとだけ心配事があって……\nあくまでちょっとしたことなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… But‚ there’s just one small thing I’m worried about…\nIt’s just a small thing though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9328342278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "些細であっても心配事は心配事だろ？\nなんでも相談してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it’s trivial‚ a worry is a worry‚ right?\nFeel free to talk to me about anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1333330552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、ありがとうございます\n最近……琴乃ちゃんが変なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ thank you.\nRecently… Kotono-chan has been acting strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2376861095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え、琴乃が変？\nつ、疲れてるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ Kotono’s been acting strange?\nI-Is she tired?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7333335639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、ある程度の疲れはあると思います\nでも近頃はぐっすり眠れてるみたいですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I think she’s probably tired to some extent.\nBut she seems to be getting a good night’s sleep lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5777105809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、学校や仕事が終わると「用事があるから」\nってそそくさと私を置いて帰っちゃうんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ when school or work ends‚ she says‚ “I have something to do‚”\nand quickly leaves me behind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2110439142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "こんなこと今までなかったんです\nどうしたのかなって心配で心配で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This has never happened before.\nI’m so worried about what happened…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4811460496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "今度寮のそばで夏祭りがあるんですけど\n一緒に行きたくても約束する暇もないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s a summer festival near the dorm coming up‚\nbut I don’t even have time to ask her to go with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1110423883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃もいろいろとやるべきことがあるんだろう\n俺は、うん、特に変だとは思わないけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess Kotono has a lot to do.\nI‚ uh‚ I don’t think it’s particularly strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9666643541,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14585.917576,
          "startTime": 83.5525819301
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですね。う～ん……とりあえずまた何か\n分かったら相談させて下さい。お疲れ様でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Hmm… Well‚ if I find out anything else‚\nI’ll let you know. Good work today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.252583456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ああ。お疲れ様……ふぅ。危ない危ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-oh. Good work… Whew. That was close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1859142463,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14114.085753699996,
          "startTime": 99.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（今度の夏のライブで、渚の誕生日サプライズをする）\n（からな。このままバレずに進めたいところだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I have to surprise Nagisa for her birthday at the next summer live.）\n（So… I want to make sure she doesn’t find out…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8666628282,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7373.3421309,
          "startTime": 102.2400049591
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　琴乃から電話か。はい、もしもし\nあぁ、順調だよ。本人にも気付かれてないし――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? A call from Kotono. Hello?\nAh‚ it’s going well. She hasn’t noticed yet――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4666694403,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.3355187999987,
          "startTime": 107.3000049591
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと忘れ物を……あ、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just forgot something… Ah‚ sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0257997672,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8607.533566100003,
          "startTime": 116.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "おわっ！？　そ、それではこの件については\nまた後ほど！　失礼します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Woah!? W-Well‚ about this matter‚\nwe’ll talk about it later! Excuse me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5666511299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん？\nそんなに慌ててどうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san?\nWhy are you in such a hurry?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6127735297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あーいや、先方がちょっとバタバタしてたんだ、ははは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Oh‚ no‚ the person on the other end was a bit busy‚ hahaha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2127735297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（……後で「急に切ってごめん」って謝らないとな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…I’ll have to apologize to her later for “suddenly hanging up”.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.8972180525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2749052841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.3749001979
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.3749001979
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりおかしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s definitely strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2415668646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "最近、なんだかみんな変な気がするんです。普通に\n話してる時でも、目配せをして急に話題を変えるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ I feel like everyone’s been acting strange. Even when we’re\ntalking normally‚ they exchange glances and suddenly change the subject…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.9082335312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.2415668646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "特におかしいのは琴乃ちゃんです！\n不自然なところがもう数えきれないくらいあるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan is especially strange!\nThere are countless unnatural things about her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6749001979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.7415668646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなのか。俺は気付かなかったけどなー\n具体的にどんなところがおかしいと思ったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-Is that so? I didn’t notice…\nSpecifically‚ what did you think was strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.366645535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_07_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "まず、私と二人で話す時に目を合わせる時間が\nいつもの半分くらいしかないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ when we talk one-on-one‚ the amount of time she\nmakes eye contact is about half of what it usually is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1530727226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.0197332858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
